I'm sure.

22
00:02:51,440 --> 00:02:53,620
Before the Master went to live in seclusion,
he left a secret trick.

23
00:02:54,170 --> 00:02:55,700
He said that if the Faction is in crisis,

24
00:02:56,100 --> 00:02:57,990
