26
00:03:04,900 --> 00:03:05,480
(I'll get it for you.)

27
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:14,120
Wow, it actually exists.

28
00:03:18,380 --> 00:03:19,210
Is this

29
00:03:19,530 --> 00:03:20,620
the legendary...

30
00:03:21,810 --> 00:03:23,260
This is the hope

31
00:03:23,750 --> 00:03:25,400
