60
00:04:53,310 --> 00:04:55,420
We can't let him win.

61
00:04:56,900 --> 00:04:57,690
Yes, sir.

62
00:04:58,450 --> 00:05:01,070
This time, the Four Emblems Faction
is coming in full force.

63
00:05:01,310 --> 00:05:02,900
As the main battlefield,
Faction 60

64
