from the Four Emblems Faction.

112
00:07:20,420 --> 00:07:21,610
What is a Challenge Order?

113
00:07:22,120 --> 00:07:24,150
I don't know. I've never heard of it.

114
00:07:25,340 --> 00:07:26,020
Never heard of it.

115
00:07:27,080 --> 00:07:28,940
An uncle of mine mentioned it before.

116
00:07:29,340 --> 00:07:31,730
This is like the declaration of war.

117
00:07:31,270 --> 00:07:37,640
Sky Earth Dark Yellow

118
00:07:32,240 --> 00:07:34,350
But our faction is only at the Level Dark.

119
00:07:34,780 --> 00:07:36,160
Generally, only the lower-level factions

120
00:07:36,160 --> 00:07:37,620
