131
00:08:03,670 --> 00:08:06,340
yet we've gone through a lot nevertheless.

132
00:08:07,300 --> 00:08:09,030
The Shadow Faction incident,

133
00:08:09,750 --> 00:08:10,880
the spiritual sword competition,

134
00:08:11,760 --> 00:08:14,550
and we also suffered losses
due to the invasion of the demons.

135
00:08:15,000 --> 00:08:17,440
However, please remember

136
00:08:17,920 --> 00:08:20,540
that justice will always prevail.

137
00:08:23,670 --> 00:08:24,500
Faction 60

138
00:08:25,150 --> 00:08:26,190
