139
00:08:27,640 --> 00:08:28,590
For today's class,

140
00:08:28,940 --> 00:08:32,500
I'll teach you the collective defense skills.

141
00:08:33,160 --> 00:08:35,800
Also, please write an essay

142
00:08:35,990 --> 00:08:37,590
