157
00:09:47,950 --> 00:09:49,770
Hahahaha.

158
00:09:50,410 --> 00:09:53,230
The game has just begun.

159
00:09:56,300 --> 00:09:59,430
Report. The fort has detected
dense spiritual signals in the Death Desert.

160
00:10:00,930 --> 00:10:04,270
He has gathered lots of pottery figurines
and is heading towards Faction 60.

161
00:10:04,920 --> 00:10:05,900
The Immortal Mobile Team

162
00:10:06,100 --> 00:10:07,860
