the emergency joint defense mechanism.

166
00:10:14,650 --> 00:10:17,190
The righteous factions will do everything

167
00:10:17,520 --> 00:10:18,530
to help the friend and stop the foe.

168
00:10:22,060 --> 00:10:24,510
Sir, this is the situation now.

169
00:10:25,030 --> 00:10:28,530
