176
00:10:52,650 --> 00:10:56,970
Everyone wants to be a friend
of the top cultivator in the Mortal Realm.

177
00:10:57,400 --> 00:10:59,930
Just rely on yourself then.

178
00:11:02,720 --> 00:11:03,700
Chief Elizabeth.

179
00:11:04,200 --> 00:11:05,000
According to the intelligence,

180
00:11:05,290 --> 00:11:07,640
Xiao Faction is now
involved in the Faction 60 affair.

181
