183
00:11:18,850 --> 00:11:21,910
I will never help the Faction 60.

184
00:11:22,580 --> 00:11:25,850
But you can't pass through here either.

185
00:11:26,940 --> 00:11:28,110
Influenced by the Knowledge Faction,

186
00:11:28,560 --> 00:11:30,970
