to help the Faction 60.

187
00:11:32,320 --> 00:11:35,670
Things are getting more and more interesting.

188
00:11:37,370 --> 00:11:38,670
This is my order.

189
00:11:39,200 --> 00:11:42,960
Send our best musician
to help the Faction 60.

190
00:11:43,180 --> 00:11:44,370
Yes, sir.

191
00:11:52,110 --> 00:11:53,020
As you can see,

192
00:11:53,450 --> 00:11:56,360
