Flash Spell.

239
00:15:07,990 --> 00:15:09,530
Amplification Spell.

240
00:15:10,040 --> 00:15:11,450
Mixed Magic Spell.

241
00:15:11,730 --> 00:15:13,100
Infinite Sword and Shield Spell.

242
00:15:17,410 --> 00:15:18,440
Stop it,

243
00:15:19,160 --> 00:15:19,950
