264
00:16:32,540 --> 00:16:33,390
The Way of Heaven?

265
00:16:40,250 --> 00:16:42,190
No...

266
00:17:01,230 --> 00:17:02,420
No wonder you're the Sword Saint.

267
00:17:02,750 --> 00:17:04,900
You hammered Xiong Wu on your own.

268
00:17:05,520 --> 00:17:06,980
I've become the stand-in.

269
00:17:09,330 --> 00:17:13,290
Have you also anticipated this?
